---
By: Shaykh Ahmad al'Alawi
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 334
    Verse: 3
Tags:
  - Nothing/Emptiness
---
One of thine attributes is pure nothingness, which belongeth unto thee and
unto the world in its entirety. If thou acknowledge thy nothingness, He
will increase thee with His being.
